        "title": "How to convert this sql in criteria hibernate?",
        "body": "<p>This is my sql<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>SELECT *\nFROM smt_aut.menu M\n  JOIN smt_aut.tela T ON M.id_menu = T.id_menu\n  JOIN smt_aut.tela_usuario TU ON T.id_tela = TU.id_tela\n  WHERE TU.id_usuario = 1;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>I tried this here but not gotta get result<\/p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<pre><code>    DetachedCriteria subQueryTU = DetachedCriteria.forClass( TelaUsuario.class, TelaUsuario_.nameQuery );\n    subQueryTU.add( Restrictions.eq( TelaUsuario_.nameQuery + \".\" + TelaUsuario_.tela + \".\" + Tela_.idTela, Tela_.nameQuery + \".\" + Tela_.idTela ) );\n    subQueryTU.add( Restrictions.eq( TelaUsuario_.nameQuery + \".\" + TelaUsuario_.usuario + \".\" + Usuario_.idUsuario, idUsuario ) );\n    subQueryTU.setProjection( Projections.property( TelaUsuario_.idTelaUsuario ) );\n\n    DetachedCriteria subQueryT = DetachedCriteria.forClass( Tela.class, Tela_.nameQuery );\n    subQueryT.add( Restrictions.eqProperty( Tela_.nameQuery + \".\" + Tela_.menu + \".\" + Menu_.idMenu, Menu_.nameQuery + \".\" + Menu_.idMenu ) );\n    subQueryT.setProjection( Projections.property( Tela_.idTela ) );\n\n    subQueryT.add( Subqueries.exists( subQueryTU ) );\n\n    Criteria criteria = this.getSession().createCriteria( Menu.class, Menu_.nameQuery );\n\n    criteria.add( Subqueries.exists( subQueryT ) );\n\n    return criteria.list();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>I want find all menus when user 1 has access, ie return all menus where there  the User has access<\/p>\n",
